item.title: Elizabeth add a quote by Kerry E. Wagner
item.description: "you don't have to worry about burning bridges, if you're building your own" -- Kerry E. Wagner

item.title: Elizabeth add a quote by Bernard M. Baruch
item.description: "Be who you are and say what you feel, because those who mind don't matter, and those who matter don't mind." -- Bernard M. Baruch

item.title: Elizabeth add a quote by Haruki Murakami
item.description: "Nobody likes being alone that much. I don't go out of my way to make friends, that's all. It just leads to disappointment. " -- Haruki Murakami

item.title: Elizabeth add a quote by Marilyn Monroe
item.description: "I'm selfish, impatient and a little insecure. I make mistakes, I am out of control and at times hard to handle. But if you can't handle me at my worst, then you sure as hell don't deserve me at my best." -- Marilyn Monroe

item.title: Elizabeth add a quote by Charles Bukowski
item.description: "Boring damned people. All over the earth. Propagating more boring damned people. What a horror show. The earth swarmed with them." -- Charles Bukowski

item.title: Elizabeth add a quote by Sam Shepard
item.description: "I had a definite sense of somehow being a passenger in an evil vehicle crusing through Paradise." -- Sam Shepard
